data.description:
Brand new 5 bedroom 3 bath house. The upper floor of this home features 3 bedrooms 2 full baths, a walk in closet in the master, Gas Fireplace, vaulted ceilings,large deck and panty in the large wrap around kitchen. The lower floor contains 2 bedrooms, one full bath a large great room and kitcenette. There is also a seperate exterior entrance a nice big patio looking onto a big yard. The home also has a two car garage and a shared laundry room. Gas heat and water heater.  New hardwood flooring in the entire house. The house is newly painted from the inside. Very close to elementary and high school, easy access to bus lines and all the major Burien shopping. Also a short drive to Southcenter and the airport. If you have an extended family or want to rent out some space to help cover the bills this home could work for you.

Neighborhood Description

This area is improving fast. Lots of new homes are being built.
